{
  "stem": "979.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He says, well, I have to think about that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we don't know what he did.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But they wrote a book about the men's orchestra, and they wrote that they were speculating whether they gonna let somebody learn the double bass.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I didn't know then until I got that book that-- here, now.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they said-- so he decided.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They decided we'd like a man from the men's orchestra come and teach me three times a week.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So they-- he got the permission.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And so this man came.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He-- he was a very-- he wasn't a double bass player, also.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He played the cello and other things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So he was very good musician.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he start teaching me an hour a week.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He had the permission.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They put up front-- you know, when you come-- men coming.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They're not supposed to come in-- that this person is going to come and teach a girl some music-- so he could get in.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Otherwise, they wouldn't let him in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he start teaching me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I found out that it wasn't so difficult.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And well, he taught me for about two months.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then the-- this SS comes back-- Hessler.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he said, where is the girl who plays the double bass?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Isn't she playing with you?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He says, what-- how do you know to play music in one minute, and in months.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She's just playing almost two months, that's all.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So-- but I learned something.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When he wasn't there I was in the other room practicing my double bass.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They gave me the piece-- piece of music that they were playing with the orchestra.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I started studying by myself for the bass.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I learned it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was following them when they were playing.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
